        "URL": "data:text/html;charset=utf-8,%3C!doctype%20html%3E%0A%3Chtml%20lang%3D%22%22%3E%0A%3Chead%3E%0A%20%20%3Cmeta%20charset%3D%22utf-8%22%3E%0A%20%20%3Ctitle%3EExit%20Press%20Release%3C%2Ftitle%3E%0A%3C%2Fhead%3E%0A%3Cbody%3E%0A%3Cbody%20bgcolor%3D%22%23000000%22%20background%3D%22..%2Fimg%2Ftile.jpg%22%20text%3D%22%23ffccff%22%20link%3D%22%2366ccff%22%20vlink%3D%22%23ff99ff%22%20alink%3D%22ff0066%22%3E%0A%3Ccenter%3E%0A%3Ctable%20border%3D%220%22%20width%3D%2290%25%22%20cellpadding%3D%220%22%3E%0A%3Ctbody%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%20align%3D%22left%22%3E%0A%3Cstrong%3E%3Cfont%20size%3D%224%22%20color%3D%22%23ff3366%22%3ETo%20be%20issued%20to%20the%20News%20Media%3C%2Ffont%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cfont%20size%3D%224%22%20color%3D%22%23ff3366%22%3E%0A%3C%2Ffont%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%0A%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%20align%3D%22right%22%3E%0A%3Cstrong%3E%3Cfont%20size%3D%224%22%20color%3D%22%23ff3366%22%3E%3Cem%3E3-22-97%3C%2Fem%3E%0A%3C%2Ffont%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%0A%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%20colspan%3D%222%22%3E%0A%3Cfont%20size%3D%224%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBy%20the%20time%20you%20read%20this%2C%20we%20suspect%20that%20%3Cem%3Ethe%20human%20bodies%20we%20were%20wearing%20have%20been%20found%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20that%20a%20flurry%20of%20fragmented%20reports%20have%20begun%20to%20hit%20the%20wire%20services.%20%20For%20those%20who%20want%20to%20know%20the%20facts%2C%20the%20following%20statement%20has%20been%20issued.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ffont%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%3C%2Ftbody%3E%3C%2Ftable%3E%0A%3Chr%20width%3D%2290%25%22%20size%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3Cstrong%3E%3Cfont%20color%3D%22ff99ff%22%20size%3D%226%22%3E%0AHEAVEN'S%20GATE%20%22Away%20Team%22%20Returns%20to%20Level%20Above%20Human%20in%20Distant%20Space%0A%3C%2Ffont%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%0A%3Chr%20width%3D%2290%25%22%20size%3D%221%22%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Ctable%20border%3D%220%22%20width%3D%2280%25%22%3E%0A%3Ctbody%3E%3Ctr%3E%0A%3Ctd%3E%0A%3Cfont%20size%3D%224%22%3E%3Cfont%20color%3D%2266ccff%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ERANCHO%20SANTO%20FE%2C%20CA%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ffont%3E%20--%20By%20the%20time%20you%20receive%20this%2C%20we'll%20be%20gone%20--%20several%20dozen%20of%20us.%20%20We%20came%20from%20the%20Level%20Above%20Human%20in%20distant%20space%20and%20we%20have%20now%20exited%20the%20bodies%20that%20we%20were%20wearing%20for%20our%20earthly%20task%2C%20to%20return%20to%20the%20world%20from%20whence%20we%20came%20--%20task%20completed.%20%20The%20distant%20space%20we%20refer%20to%20is%20what%20your%20religious%20literature%20would%20call%20the%20Kingdom%20of%20Heaven%20or%20the%20Kingdom%20of%20God.%3Cp%3E%0A%0AWe%20came%20for%20the%20purpose%20of%20offering%20a%20doorway%20to%20the%20Kingdom%20of%20God%20at%20the%20end%20of%20this%20civilization%2C%20the%20end%20of%20this%20age%2C%20the%20end%20of%20this%20millenium.%20%20We%20came%20from%20that%20Level%2C%20that%20time%2C%20that%20space%2C%20and%20entered%20this%20one.%20%20And%20in%20so%20doing%2C%20we%20had%20to%20enter%20human%20bodies%20--%20which%20we%20did%2C%20for%20the%20most%20part%2C%20in%20the%20mid-seventies.%20%20Now%20it%20was%20time%20for%20us%20to%20leave%20those%20bodies%20(vehicles)%20--%20bodies%20that%20we%20borrowed%20for%20the%20time%20we%20were%20here%20(by%20previous%20arrangement)%20for%20this%20specific%20task.%20%20The%20task%20was%20not%20only%20to%20bring%20in%20information%20about%20that%20Evolutionary%20Kingdom%20Level%20Above%20Human%2C%20but%20to%20give%20us%20the%20experience%20of%20working%20against%20the%20forces%20of%20what%20the%20human%20evolutionary%20level%2C%20at%20this%20time%2C%20has%20become.%20%20And%20while%20it%20was%20a%20good%20learning%20experience%20for%20us%2C%20it%20also%20gave%20all%20who%20ever%20received%20knowledge%20from%20that%20Kingdom%20an%20opportunity%20to%20recognize%20us%20and%20this%20information%2C%20and%20to%20even%20move%20out%20of%20the%20human%20level%20and%20into%20the%20Next%20Level%20or%20the%20Next%20Evolutionary%20Level%2C%20the%20%22Kingdom%20of%20Heaven%2C%22%20the%20Kingdom%20of%20God.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%0AThe%20Kingdom%20of%20God%2C%20the%20Level%20Above%20Human%2C%20is%20a%20physical%20world%2C%20where%20they%20inhabit%20physical%20bodies.%20%20However%2C%20those%20bodies%20are%20merely%20containers%2C%20suits%20of%20clothes%20--%20the%20%3Cem%3Etrue%20identity%3C%2Fem%3E%20(of%20the%20individual)%20is%20the%20soul%20or%20mind%2Fspirit%20residing%20in%20that%20%22vehicle.%22%20%20The%20body%20is%20merely%20a%20tool%20for%20that%20individual's%20use%20--%20when%20it%20wears%20out%2C%20he%20is%20issued%20a%20new%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%20%20%0ANo%20one%20can%20enter%20the%20Kingdom%20of%20Heaven%20by%20trying%20to%20live%20a%20good%20life%20in%20this%20world%2C%20and%20then%2C%20thinking%20that%20when%20this%20world's%20life%20takes%20your%20body%2C%20you%20get%20to%20%22go%20to%20heaven.%22%20%20The%20%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3Eonly%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20time%20that%20Next%20Kingdom%20can%20be%20entered%20is%20when%20there%20is%20a%20Member%20or%20Members%20of%20that%20Kingdom%20who%20have%20come%20into%20the%20human%20kingdom%2C%20incarnated%20as%20we%20have%2C%20offering%20clarification%20of%20that%20information.%20%20To%20get%20into%20a%20discarnate%20condition%20just%20by%20disconnecting%20from%20your%20body%20doesn't%20mean%20that%20you%20are%20going%20to%20go%20anywhere%2C%20whether%20that%20loss%20of%20body%20is%20%22premature%22%20or%20not.%20%20When%20we%20step%20out%20of%20our%20%22vehicle%2C%22%20we%20have%20to%20know%20where%20and%20who%20our%20%22tour%20guide%22%20(our%20Shepherd)%20is%20--%20for%20what's%20next.%20%20We%20have%20to%20know%20we%20can%20connect%20with%20a%20Shepherd%20whom%20we%20trust%2C%20and%20that%20we%20have%20decided%2C%20%22If%20that%20Shepherd%20will%20have%20me%2C%20I%20want%20to%20continue%20to%20be%20a%20sheep%20--%20and%20I%20will%20do%20everything%20I%20can%20to%20please%20that%20Shepherd.%22%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%20%0APeriodically%2C%20that%20Next%20Level%20sends%20in%20a%20Representative%20--%20a%20Shepherd%20--%20and%20offers%20a%20graduation%20class%2C%20offers%20life%2C%20out%20of%20this%20evolutionary%20level%20into%20that%20Next%20Evolutionary%20Level%2C%20and%20we%20are%20at%20the%20end%20of%20one%20of%20those%20times.%20%20TI%20and%20DO%20were%20the%20names%20used%20by%20the%20Representatives%20of%20that%20Next%20Level%2C%20the%20Kingdom%20of%20God%2C%20sent%20to%20the%20%22surface%22%20of%20this%20planet%20to%20serve%20as%20our%20Teachers%2F%22Midwives%22%20at%20this%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%0ADuring%20a%20brief%20window%20of%20time%2C%20some%20may%20wish%20to%20follow%20us.%20%20If%20they%20do%2C%20it%20will%20not%20be%20easy.%20%20The%20requirement%20is%20to%20not%20only%20believe%20who%20the%20Representatives%20are%2C%20but%2C%20to%20do%20as%20they%20and%20we%20did.%20%20You%20must%20leave%20%3Cem%3Eeverything%3C%2Fem%3E%20of%20your%20humanness%20behind.%20%20This%20includes%20the%20ultimate%20sacrifice%20and%20demonstration%20of%20faith%20--%20that%20is%2C%20the%20shedding%20of%20your%20human%20body.%20%20If%20you%20should%20choose%20to%20do%20this%2C%20logistically%20it%20is%20preferred%20that%20you%20make%20this%20exit%20somewhere%20in%20the%20area%20of%20the%20West%20or%20Southwest%20of%20the%20United%20States%20--%20but%20if%20this%20is%20not%20possible%20--%20it%20is%20not%20required.%20%20You%20must%20call%20on%20the%20name%20of%20TI%20and%20DO%20to%20assist%20you.%20%20In%20so%20doing%2C%20you%20will%20engage%20a%20communication%20of%20sorts%2C%20alerting%20a%20spacecraft%20to%20your%20location%20where%20you%20will%20be%20picked%20up%20after%20shedding%20your%20vehicle%2C%20and%20taken%20to%20another%20world%20--%20by%20members%20of%20the%20Kingdom%20of%20Heaven.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%0AOnly%20a%20Member%20of%20the%20Next%20Level%20can%20give%20you%20Life%20--%20can%20take%20you%20out%20of%20%22Death%22%20--%20but%20it%20requires%20that%20you%20disconnect%2C%20separate%2C%20from%20the%20last%20element%20holding%20you%20to%20the%20human%20kingdom.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%0AWe%20know%20what%20we're%20saying%20--%20we%20know%20it%20requires%20a%20%22leap%20of%20faith.%22%20%20But%20it's%20deliberate%20--%20designed%20for%20those%20who%20would%20rather%20take%20that%20leap%20than%20stay%20in%20this%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%0AWe%20suggest%20that%20anyone%20serious%20about%20considering%20this%20go%20into%20their%20most%20quiet%20place%20and%20ask%2C%20scream%2C%20with%20all%20of%20their%20being%2C%20directing%20their%20asking%20to%20the%20Highest%20Source%20they%20can%20imagine%20(beyond%20Earth's%20atmosphere)%2C%20to%20give%20them%20guidance.%20%20Only%20those%20%22chosen%22%20by%20that%20Next%20Kingdom%20will%20%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3Eknow%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20that%20this%20is%20right%20for%20them%2C%20and%20will%20be%20given%20the%20courage%20required%20to%20act.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffont%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cfont%20size%3D%224%22%3E%0A%3C%2Ffont%3E%0A%0A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ccenter%3E%0A%3Cstrong%3E%3Cfont%20size%3D%225%22%20color%3D%2266ccff%22%3ESOME%20RELEVANT%20SCRIPTURES%3C%2Ffont%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%0A%3C%2Fcenter%3E%0A%3Cp%3E%0A%0A%3Cfont%20size%3D%224%22%3E%3C%2Ffont%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cfont%20size%3D%224%22%3E%0A%3Cli%3ETherefore%20doth%20my%20Father%20love%20me%2C%20because%20I%20lay%20down%20my%20life%2C%20that%20I%20might%20take%20it%20again.%20%20No%20man%20taketh%20it%20from%20me%2C%20but%20I%20lay%20it%20down%20of%20myself.%20%20I%20have%20power%20to%20lay%20it%20down%2C%20and%20I%20have%20power%20to%20take%20it%20again.%20%20This%20commandment%20have%20I%20received%20of%20my%20Father.%20%20JOHN%2010%3A15--18%3Cp%3E%0A%20%0A%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20that%20believeth%20on%20me%2C%20the%20works%20that%20I%20do%20shall%20he%20do%20also%3A%20%20JOHN%2014%3A12%3Cp%3E%0A%20%0A%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAnd%20except%20that%20the%20Lord%20shorten%20those%20days%2C%20none%20shall%20be%20saved%3A%20but%20for%20the%20elect's%20sake%2C%20whom%20He%20has%20chosen%2C%20He%20hath%20shortened%20the%20days.%20%20MARK%2013%3A20%3Cp%3E%0A%20%0A%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20who%20loves%20his%20life%20will%20lose%20it%2C%20and%20he%20who%20hates%20his%20life%20in%20this%20world%20will%20keep%20it%20for%20eternal%20life.%20%20JOHN%2012%3A25%3Cp%3E%0A%20%0A%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBlessed%20are%20the%20dead%20who%20die%20in%20the%20Lord.%20%20REVELATION%2014%3A13%3Cp%3E%0A%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ffont%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%0A%3C%2Ftr%3E%0A%3C%2Ftbody%3E%3C%2Ftable%3E%0A%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fcenter%3E%0A%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cbr%3E%0A%0A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ccenter%3E%3Cimg%3E%3C%2Fcenter%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ccenter%3E%3Cimg%3E%3C%2Fcenter%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Ccenter%3E%0AFor%20subsequent%20topics%20return%20to%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%22..%2Findex.html%23keys%22%3E%0A%3Cstrong%3E%7C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Home%20Page%20Bookmarks%20%3Cstrong%3E%7C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cbr%3E%20%0ATo%20Access%20Our%20Online%20Book%20%3Ca%20href%3D%22..%2Fbook%2Fbook.htm%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%7C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%0AHow%20and%20When%20HEAVEN'S%20GATE%20May%20Be%20Entered%20%3Cstrong%3E%7C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%0A%3Cp%3E%0ATo%20Send%20Us%20an%20Email%20Use%3Cstrong%3E%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%26nbsp%3B%0A%3Ca%20href%3D%22mailto%3Arep%40heavensgate.com%22%3E%20%0Arep%40heavensgate.com%3C%2Fa%3E%0A%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fcenter%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%0A%0A%3C%2Fbody%3E%0A%3C%2Fbody%3E%0A%3C%2Fhtml%3E"
